    Interface Description
    DBListener<T>
    DBListener is an interface made to process data returned asynchronously from the database.

    Class Description
    CircleBitmap
    A class that contains the static method that takes a bitmap and turns it into a circular bitmap.
    Dashboard  
    DBActive
    A class designed to collect data pertaining to an active user to be used by the database manager and facilitate interactions with the database.
    DBGroup
    A class designed to collect data pertaining to a group to be used by the database manager and facilitate interactions with the database.
    DBManager
    The sole point of communication between the rest of the app and Firebase's realtime database.
    DBMessage
    A class designed to collect data pertaining to a single message to be used by the database manager and facilitate interactions with the database.
    DBUser
    A class designed to collect data pertaining to a user to be used by the database manager and facilitate interactions with the database.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
